<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA521_05_IH_0006</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <!-- <script src="../../common_practice/js/ema521_01_02_ih.js"></script> -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema521_05.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema521_05_ih_0006 paging">
      <section class="title type2 score">
        <h2 data-head="6" class="is_star" lang="y">서하는 21500원짜리 책을 1000원짜리 지폐로만 계산하려고 합니다. 물음에 답해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>
      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <div class="img_row">
            <div class="img_area flex justify_center">
              <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA521_05_IH/0006_01.png" alt="" />
              <p lang="y">21500원</p>
            </div>

            <div class="question_box justify_center dir_col mt_30">
              <h3 lang="y">최소 얼마를 내야 하는지 구해 보세요.</h3>
              <div class="input_area mt_30">
                <span>(</span>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="22000"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span lang="y">)원</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">
                    책을 1000원짜리 지폐로만 계산하려면 책의 값을 올림하여 천의 자리까지 나타내야 합니다. <br />
                    21<span class="text_bg_red">500</span> ➔ 22000 <br />
                    따라서 최소 22000원을 내야 합니다.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <div class="img_row">
            <div class="img_area flex justify_center">
              <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA521_05_IH/0006_01.png" alt="" />
              <p lang="y">21500원</p>
            </div>

            <div class="question_box justify_center dir_col mt_30">
              <h3 lang="y">1000원짜리 지폐를 최소 몇 장 내야 하는지 구해 보세요.</h3>
              <div class="input_area mt_30">
                <span>(</span>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="22"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span lang="y">)장</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">22000원을 내려면 1000원짜리 지폐를 22장 내야 합니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
